query_valid_al

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_valid_al -  This method determines if the alignment is valid for the deity.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_valid_al(string deity,
int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^deity%^RESET%^ - the deity to check
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the alignment to check
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
0 if it is valid, 1 if above upper_al, -1 if lower than lower_al

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/deity_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method determines if the alignment is valid for the deity.
.EP

